==English==

===Etymology===
Old French ''[[paraclet]]'', from Late Latin ''[[paraclet]]'', from Greek [[παρακλητος]] ‘call in aid’ (from [[καλεω]] ‘call’).

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/'pæɹəkli:t/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# an [[advocate]], especially the [[Holy Spirit]]
